#### 6. Magic Number Test *(Smell #6 — testsmells.org)*

**Method:** `CalculateTotal_ReturnsCorrectAmount` (line 69)
**Problem:** `247.50m`, `22.28m`, `269.78m` — where do these numbers come from? A reader must reverse-engineer the pricing logic to verify them.

